snippet.title: Live Coding: Python Honeypot
snippet.description:
Let's build a Python honeypot! The goal is to build a simple Honeypot that logs whenever TCP connections are detected. We'll package it up for pip and pypi, and also as a .deb to install properly as a systemd service, with configs in /etc/ and logs in /var/log/.
